                                        <li>Track temperature and humidity changes</li>
                                        <li>Monitor VPD (Vapor Pressure Deficit) for optimal growing conditions</li>
                                        <li>Record lighting schedules and intensity</li>
                                        <li>Log water and nutrient amounts</li>
                                        <li>Identify patterns and trends over time</li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <div class="alert alert-success">
